;----------------------------------------------
;Lower nybble:
;To convert from binary to ASCII we only need to add 7 if value is more than 9:
;or $f0     ;Remains the same
;daa        ;Adds 6 if more than 9
;add a,$a0  ;If DAA added 6 then this will set carry (see high nybble section)
